The road to Hell's paved for us. Guess I missed
Receiving what keeps others from killing
What they wished they deserved (but can't). Ruthless
Would be a better name for these dealings
In baths and misguided gifts of meat stuffs.
What mean gods might've made so worst a wife?
What door(s) might shut to replace your best knife?
